{"tid":2281751,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"今日(2020年11月11日)唔係最黑暗嘅一日囉","createTime":"2020-11-11T10:53:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-11T10:59:20.000Z","uid":295459,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cad5b0ef1fce1b328c941cfaa7b20450bf03b045","tid":2281751,"uid":295459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T10:53:53.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"gold\">今日之前<br />\n日撚日都係咁黑暗架啦<br />\n<br />\n泛民終於肯總辭<br />\n算係有返一點好微細嘅光明<br />\n所以唔係最黑暗嘅一日</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">未來有幾黑暗得幾黑暗呀<br />\n我已經心理上準備好槍口對準中共<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/darkness.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/threat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a975b083d1478f94fe521da1e7d73b5145c3364","tid":2281751,"uid":295459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T10:59:20.000Z","msg":"自推<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}